Package: LISdmr
Type: Package
Title: LIS-based DMR Detetion Method
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Xiaoyu Dai <xiaoyu.dai@go.wustl.edu>
Maintainer: Xiaoyu Dai <xiaoyu.dai@go.wustl.edu>
Description: DMR detection using MeDIP-seq and MRE-seq data. The DMC status is modeled by a Conditional Random Field (CRF), and rejection are made based on each local index of significance (LIS).
